{
  "texts": [
    "Access to the GPT models was provided through the MSHS Azure tenant environment using the OpenAI API.",
    "Llama, Qwen, Gemma and Phi models were accessed via a 4xH100 80GB local MSH cluster through the Hugging Face interface.",
    "Default model settings were used for all the models.",
    "To create code description embeddings, the GIST-large-embedding-v0 model was utilized, as it has been identified as effective for clinical tasks in a previous study.",
    "11 The model embedded all ICD descriptions assigned across MSHS EDs through 2023."
  ]
}